item.title: Living
item.description: Photo by Joel Oliveira on Unsplash Somewhere in the Yucatan channel, where the Gulf of Mexico meets the Caribbean sea, lies a very happy crocodile named Lorenzo. His daily routine includes swimming upto a lagoon, seeing his human friend (lets call him Diego) and getting lots of lobster in return. He is a visibly happy and chubby crocodile; so adorable that he’s become an integral experience for the lagoon’s visitors.
